61 telecommunications or any of their respective general
62 contractors or subcontractors, provided the work is performed
63 under the supervision of a licensed architect or engineer.
64 (6) Routine or regular maintenance, repair,
65 replacement, reinstallation, or removal of equipment,
66 specialized technological processes, or equipment facility
67 systems as determined by the board with regard to scope,
